  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "BIM Modeler",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Ensure projects are completed in accordance to BIM guidelines and compliance with the relevant government regulatory requirements</p></li><li><p>Generate detailed plan, elevation, section, and detail drawings from the models, including sufficient detail and proper annotation for tender and construction purposes</p></li><li><p>Deliver appropriate visuals and shop drawings to support construction works</p></li><li><p>Manage process of coordination, exchange of data and collaboration of BIM with project stakeholders</p></li><li><p>Work in accordance with project scope and schedule, and ensure accuracy</p></li><li><p>Ensure models and/or drawings produced to comply with applicable codes, standards and specifications</p></li><li><p>Manage processes, implementation, best practices and techniques of BIM and related tools</p></li><li><p>Able to assist on documentation for record and submission related to BIM processes</p></li><li><p>Perform all duties in accordance with company’s polices, processes, systems, reporting and procedures.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Preferably with at least 5 years experience working with BIM related software or BIM modelling works</p></li><li><p>Able to work independently with minimum supervision</p></li><li><p>Proficient in Revit/BIM software for Archi and Structure MEP</p></li><li><p>Familiar with Singapore Construction Industry regulations</p></li><li><p>Prefer those with tender experiences</p></li><li><p>Near Jurong East Mrt</p></li></ul>",
